The evidence with the title 'The amount of debt is on pace to double in five years and triple in 10 ' says Jan 28, 2010  ... McDonnell 's claim that the debt is on pace to double in five years and triple in 10 is not a new talking point for Republicans . Judd Gregg (the Republican senator from New Hampshire who was almost Obama 's commerce secretary) said the same thing about Obama 's proposed 2010 budget last march. 
